{"type": "article", "id": 22518, "title": "金属和大理石组合调料瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-19T07:10:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004242PHhYc2TdLKkrop5U.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组调料瓶，来自美国女设计师 Anna Rabinowicz 自创的品牌 Anna New York。她使用了金属和大理石的经典搭配，圆筒形的瓶身上放着半圆大理石盖子，不同材料之间在颜色、纹路和质感上都有一个反差，但维持了巧妙的平衡，带有古典色彩。可以选择不锈钢灰、玫瑰金和金色三种，售价 185 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.annanewyork.com/collections/tabletop/products/amare-serving-set\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004239heZqK2TRNwmosrCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.77333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042403ncF41a9vINihKfC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042408GPLRKWsav5S7h3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004240os1CXVMKrfUq9FZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004241EfYFXbp0GSwcKVtk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}